CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 21, 1946, pg. 25, reads: "'General' Lee at Pitt - Following in the footsteps of Jimmy Joe Robinson, Pitt's backfield ace last season, is Bobby (General) Lee, former New Castle High star.  Here Coach Wes Fesler, who was a teammate of Bill Bell at Ohio State, shows the 'General' how to hold the pigskin.  Robinson is now in the Army. - Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Football coach Wes Fesler handing football to University of Pittsburgh football player Bobby "General" Lee in Pitt Stadium
